{
  "stem": "7860.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because a proper way for me would be, as anybody would be in the United States, I come to the present house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I would say, good morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I used to be beaten up because I was recognized because I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And later on, I realized that by following professional beggars, gentiles, that when they come into the house, they say, bless Jesus Christ.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Poles would say forever and ever on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I did this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then things got better for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then many Jewish people-- I thought I had an exclusive on this thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because many other people do the same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I-- they used to ask me to cross myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I had to learn how to cross myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I used to be beaten up then too because I crossed myself the wrong shoulders, until I mastered it the proper way.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And also then later, they got more sophisticated-- asked you to say the Polish prayer known as [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I stole a little catechism by a peasant's house, and I learned the [NON-ENGLISH] from the front page and memorized the prayer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Before I learned the prayer, many nights I had to sleep over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I got stuck at night and they let you sleep over in their house, the peasants.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Straw bed-- you down on straw on the cement floor, they had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so I play my part leaning in front of a statue or in front of a picture, holy picture.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I used to cross myself, mumble with my lips a little bit, pretend I'm playing, and cross myself again and went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the peasant always would watch me if I'm doing it right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they were kind of proud of me that I'm good.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
